        config = configs[job_id]
        config.seed += job_id
        print(config)
        store["config"] = dataclasses.asdict(config)
        store["log"] = {}

        try:
            config.run(store=store)
        except Exception:
            store["exception"] = traceback.format_exc()
            raise
